data.description: Embrace the potential of this charming 2-bed, 1-bath starter home in Yelm. Just shy of a quarter acre near downtown, this single-story residence awaits your personal touch. With a little TLC, this home can transform into your dream haven. The property includes a backyard shed, offering endless possibilities for hobby space or additional storage. Conveniently located, enjoy easy access to local amenities. The well-designed floor plan maximizes space, creating a comfortable living environment. Picture yourself entertaining in the spacious backyard or unwinding on the porch. Affordable and promising, this home is your canvas for creativity and homeownership in Yelm's sought-after community. Seize the opportunity to make this house your own!
